name: Moonlight Drive vol. 2
description:
"Moonlight Drive vol.2" by Jesse Robin

Original embroidered applique art mix-tape.
Handmade in England with love by me using vintage fabrics, buttons & a typewriter. 

Mounted & framed in a stylish modern white box frame, with glass
suitable for hanging or standing.
Frame size 8" x 10" (20cm x 25.5cm)
Picture size 3.5" x 5.5" (9cm x 14cm)

These can be made to order with your choice of song title/message & colour palette.
Ideal gift for a wedding presant with first dance song or for someone special with 'your song'

Packaged with reused bubblewrap & polystyrene for added postal protection. Sent using Royal Mail next day Special delivery.
